        <abstract>
            <p>Believes that species or genus may have originated more than once from separate ancestors, i.e., polyphyletically.</p> 
<p>Discusses relation of CD’s theory to religion. Has written popular account of CD’s theory in Dutch [<hi rend="italic">Darwin en de Godsdienst</hi> (1869)].</p> 
        </abstract>
